Create website with DevOps Tools 

Step 1 :- Go to any cloud provider GCP 
Step 2 :- Create Virtual machine 
Step 3 :- install docker 
				sudo -i
				apt-get update
				apt install docker.io
				docker -v

Docker version 24.0.7, build 24.0.7-0ubuntu2~20.04.1

done 


Step 4 :- Download website from https://www.free-css.com/ 
		            wget 
	                  apt install unzip
done 

Step 5 :- Run the nginx container with downloaded website 
	docker run -ti -d -p 80:80 -v /root/inance-html:/usr/share/nginx/html nginx

Step 6 :- Go to IP address:80 and verify


